    {
      "id": "zcU2o89l70kb6TXn3A3I9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -409.05004998496577,
      "y": 1007.2585835473747,
      "width": 587.7593994140625,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "1lUtkSrt7OZaZn4WGmGeE",
      "index": "b25l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 298882810,
      "version": 1092,
      "versionNonce": 1773242938,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780994292313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\nprompt: \"Explain the kuberenetes ..... \"\n\n> tokenizer = [t1, t2 , ....... , tn]\n\n> blockhashing = [f(t1), f(t2, f(t1)) ..... f(tn, Hn-1)]\n\nso each block has context of the previous block \nstarting with h1 , h2 has h1, h3 has h2, h1 \n\nso the block is distributed across shards for token \nefficiency even if h1 is missing we can restore it using h10\n\nwe check [h1, h2 , hn] block is already cache in the bitmap\nusing fibonacci binary search if yes we return the pods that\nare available to the filter stage \n\nex : [pod A, pod b, pod C] ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nprompt: \"Explain the kuberenetes ..... \"\n\n> tokenizer = [t1, t2 , ....... , tn]\n\n> blockhashing = [f(t1), f(t2, f(t1)) ..... f(tn, Hn-1)]\n\nso each block has context of the previous block \nstarting with h1 , h2 has h1, h3 has h2, h1 \n\nso the block is distributed across shards for token \nefficiency even if h1 is missing we can restore it using h10\n\nwe check [h1, h2 , hn] block is already cache in the bitmap\nusing fibonacci binary search if yes we return the pods that\nare available to the filter stage \n\nex : [pod A, pod b, pod C] ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
