    {
      "id": "bdVsAfxLIjfqOBF1DWv1K",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1113.1057526782051,
      "y": 1003.4482235925412,
      "width": 565.279541015625,
      "height": 550,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "DOH3Q11BEpqtYpj42KZOv",
      "index": "b2A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 882897382,
      "version": 2197,
      "versionNonce": 963706598,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781006676083,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\npods = [pod B, pod C]\n\nscore will be based on \n\nsessionscore = if sessionAffinity key already exist\nscore 1 else 0\n\ncahceScore = score the pod with maximum cache to avoid \nrecomputation\n\nleastLoad =  analyze the load to each pod and finalize \nscore higher if least load \n\n \n\n\n       \n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\npods = [pod B, pod C]\n\nscore will be based on \n\nsessionscore = if sessionAffinity key already exist\nscore 1 else 0\n\ncahceScore = score the pod with maximum cache to avoid \nrecomputation\n\nleastLoad =  analyze the load to each pod and finalize \nscore higher if least load \n\n \n\n\n       \n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
