      "seed": 1708251130,
      "version": 2874,
      "versionNonce": 1547011494,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781006993416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n now the scored results will arrive here  \n {\n    podB : 1 ,\n    podC : 0.70\n  } \n\n\nhere podB is higher, so the traffic will be routed to B\nand process it and return kc cache to decode pod later \n\nthe picker stage outputs the dispatch = single or \ndisaggregateed\n       \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n now the scored results will arrive here  \n {\n    podB : 1 ,\n    podC : 0.70\n  } \n\n\nhere podB is higher, so the traffic will be routed to B\nand process it and return kc cache to decode pod later \n\nthe picker stage outputs the dispatch = single or \ndisaggregateed\n       \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "suKaKCFwc1_4tizUXLRDU",
